{"article_id":"nlDpjaqz1F2969Ah","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US President Donald Trump has admitted","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"his son met a Russian lawyer in June 2016","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"`` to get information on an opponent '' ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"but argues","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"it was legal .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Donald Trump Jr 's meeting with Kremlin-linked lawyer Natalia Veselnitskaya at Trump Tower could constitute a breach of US campaign rules ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"experts say .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"And the meeting is being investigated by Special Counsel Robert Mueller as part of his inquiry into Russia 's alleged role","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"to help Mr Trump win .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"He has called the ongoing investigations in the US `` the greatest political witch hunt in history '' .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Russia has repeatedly denied claims","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"it interfered in the November 2016 presidential elections ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"where Mr Trump defeated Democratic rival Hillary Clinton .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"On Sunday , US media","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"including the Washington Post , CNN and AP","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"reported","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"that Mr Trump was worried","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Donald Trump Jr could be in legal trouble","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"because of the 9 June 2016 meeting with Ms Veselnitskaya in New York .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"They cited several unnamed sources .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"Mr Trump tweeted :","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"`` Fake News reporting , a complete fabrication ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that I am concerned about the meeting","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"my wonderful son , Donald , had in Trump Tower . ``","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"This was a meeting","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"to get information on an opponent ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"totally legal","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"and done all the time in politics","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"- and it went nowhere .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"On Monday , the president quoted a Fox and Friends interview about alleged Democratic collusion with Russia .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Mr Trump has spoken out before about links between Moscow and Mrs Clinton","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"while saying","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"it is `` commonly agreed '' that there was no collusion between Russia and him .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Mr Trump 's Sunday tweet appears to contradict a previous statement from the Trump camp about the meeting .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"When the meeting was first reported by the New York Times ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Donald Trump Jr said in a statement","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"that he and Ms Veselnitskaya had mostly discussed a suspended programme for Americans","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"to adopt Russian children .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"However , he subsequently admitted","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"he had agreed to the meeting","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"after being told he would be offered information","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"that would prove detrimental to Mrs Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"He also released the email exchange","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"that brought about the meeting .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"US media then reported","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"that the US president had been involved in the initial statement","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"his son issued on the meeting .","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"This was initially denied by Mr Trump 's team ,","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"but his lawyers later confirmed","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"that he had in fact dictated his son 's statement .","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"US commentators have argued","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"that Mr Trump 's new admission","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"that the meeting was to gain information about Mrs Clinton","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"shows","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"that the earlier statement was misleading .","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"Mr Trump again denied knowing about the meeting in Sunday 's tweet .","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"8 July 2017 :","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"The New York Times reveals","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"the June 2016 meeting took place","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"and Mr Trump Jr releases a statement","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"describing it as a `` short introductory meeting ''","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"that focused on Russian adoptions","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"The New York Times reveals","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"the June 2016 meeting took place","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"and Mr Trump Jr releases a statement","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"describing it as a `` short introductory meeting ''","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"that focused on Russian adoptions","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"9 July 2017 :","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"The Times reports","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"that Mr Trump Jr was promised damaging information about Hillary Clinton before the meeting .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"He confirmed the report","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"but said in a second statement","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"that `` no meaningful information '' came from the meeting","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"The Times reports","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"that Mr Trump Jr was promised damaging information about Hillary Clinton before the meeting .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"He confirmed the report","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"but said in a second statement","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"that `` no meaningful information '' came from the meeting","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"11 July 2017 :","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Mr Trump Jr tweets screenshots of his email correspondence","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"that discussed setting up the meeting","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"just minutes before the email chain was revealed in a Times story .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"The emails showed","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"he was eager to accept `` sensitive '' information","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"that was `` part of Russia and its government 's support for Mr Trump '' :","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"Mr Trump Jr tweets screenshots of his email correspondence","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"that discussed setting up the meeting","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"just minutes before the email chain was revealed in a Times story .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"The emails showed","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"he was eager to accept `` sensitive '' information","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"that was `` part of Russia and its government 's support for Mr Trump ''","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"12-16 July 2017 :","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"The president 's lawyer Jay Sekulow denies","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"that Mr Trump was involved in his son 's initial statement to the Times","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"The president 's lawyer Jay Sekulow denies","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"that Mr Trump was involved in his son 's initial statement to the Times","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"2 June 2018 :","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"The Times reports","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"that Mr Trump 's lawyers wrote a letter to special counsel Mueller","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"acknowledging","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"that he dictated his son 's initial statement","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"The Times reports","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"that Mr Trump 's lawyers wrote a letter to special counsel Mueller","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"acknowledging","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"that he dictated his son 's initial statement","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"26 July 2018 :","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"The president 's former personal lawyer Michael Cohen says","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"that Mr Trump approved the June 2016 meeting ,","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"contradicting previous statements by the Trump legal team","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"The president 's former personal lawyer Michael Cohen says","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"that Mr Trump approved the June 2016 meeting ,","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"contradicting previous statements by the Trump legal team","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"5 August 2018 :","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"The president says","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"his son took the meeting `` to get information on an opponent '' ,","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"but denies having any knowledge of it","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"Last month , however , Mr Trump 's former lawyer Michael Cohen said","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"the president knew about the meeting in advance .","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"The special counsel is currently investigating","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"whether Mr Trump obstructed justice .","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"Under US law , obstruction cases require proving `` corrupt intent '' -","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"so","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"while Mr Trump 's tweet does not prove anything illegal ,","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"it could serve as evidence of the president 's intent .","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"It is common for US politicians to research their opponents during a campaign .","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"However , legal experts say","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"that Mr Trump Jr could fall foul of campaign finance laws ,","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"which prohibit accepting anything of value from a foreign government or foreign national .","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"Mr Trump Jr 's apparently enthusiastic response to the offer of information about Mrs Clinton could also breach conspiracy laws .","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"The Trump team has argued","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"that Mr Trump Jr ultimately did not receive any damaging information about Mrs Clinton at the meeting .","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"Some analysts say","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"that","depth":15},{"id":133,"text":"by having the meeting at all ,","depth":16},{"id":134,"text":"Mr Trump Jr broke the law .","depth":16},{"id":135,"text":"But others say","depth":15},{"id":136,"text":"it is unclear","depth":15},{"id":137,"text":"as no information reportedly exchanged hands at the meeting .","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"One of Mr Trump 's lawyers , Jay Sekulow , said on Sunday","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"that the meeting had not broken any laws .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"`` The question is what law , statute or rule or regulation 's been violated ?","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"Nobody 's pointed to one , ''","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"Mr Sekulow told ABC News .","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"US media reported last year","depth":2},{"id":144,"text":"that some of the president 's advisers feared","depth":3},{"id":145,"text":"the extent of the president 's intervention could place him and some of his inner circle in legal jeopardy .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":291,"left":288,"right":290,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":158,"right":287,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":158,"left":150,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":148,"right":149,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":0,"right":147,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":147,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":154,"right":156,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":151,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":10,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"N